data.description: MOTIVATED SELLERS--Welcome HOME to this Luxury Modern Farmhouse Style Home in the Country! A total of 4,660 finished square feet that was originally built in 2006 with no expenses spared! Your Dream Covered Front Porch. Custom Kitchen Cabinetry and Granite Countertops in the Kitchen. 2 Gas Fireplace's in both the living room area and the kitchen. Pantry! Main Level Laundry Room. The crawl space features a 1/2 basement wall for height for easy access. 50 year rated shingles! Outdoor Hardy Wood Stove for the furnace and water heater! There are 2 HVAC systems due to the size of this home, however using the Hardy Stove allows you to have very minimal utility costs! Country living on 2 acres of land, but only 5 minutes to the Interstate! Pool and Patio Area make for a great Entertaining Space! Attached Garage features high ceilings allowing you additional storage space. There's also a detached garage 24 x 30 providing you with an additional 720 square feet that is currently heated/cooled and used as a photography studio- it could easily be utilized as a garage again or would make an ideal office suite for you!
